this wouldn't happen.

1004
01:19:08,958 --> 01:19:12,999
Poor guy.
He's an old guy who's sick.

1005
01:19:13,791 --> 01:19:17,165
Is this everything?
Nothing else in his pockets? Are you sure?

1006
01:19:17,250 --> 01:19:19,665
Poor guy. Is it true
