that's willing to expose himself for us.

1017
01:19:49,041 --> 01:19:50,665
Come on, Nina! Wake up.

1018
01:19:50,750 --> 01:19:53,124
We've got to get rid of him.

1019
01:19:53,208 --> 01:19:56,749
